<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Privacy Policy | FixOra</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  </head>

  <body class="bg-slate-50 text-slate-800">
    <%- include("../partials/toast.ejs") %>
    <!-- HEADER INCLUDE -->
    <%- include("../partials/client/header.ejs") %>
    <!-- HERO -->
    <section class="bg-slate-900 text-white py-16">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-3">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="text-indigo-100 text-sm">Last updated: <%= new Date().toDateString() %></p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CONTENT -->
    <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-14">
      <div class="bg-white border rounded-2xl shadow-sm p-8 space-y-8 leading-relaxed">
        <!-- INTRO -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">1. Introduction</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-600">
            FixOra respects your privacy and is committed to protecting your personal data. This
            policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- DATA COLLECTED -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">2. Information We Collect</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc ml-6 text-slate-600 space-y-1">
            <li>Name, phone number, email address</li>
            <li>Service address and booking details</li>
            <li>Payment and transaction information</li>
            <li>Device, browser, and usage analytics</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- USE -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">3. How We Use Your Data</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc ml-6 text-slate-600 space-y-1">
            <li>To process bookings and payments</li>
            <li>To connect you with verified technicians</li>
            <li>To improve platform performance and security</li>
            <li>To send booking updates or support messages</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- SHARING -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">4. Data Sharing</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-600">
            We only share necessary information with technicians assigned to your booking, payment
            providers, and legal authorities if required by law. We never sell your personal data.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- STORAGE -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">5. Data Security</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-600">
            We implement industry-standard security measures including encrypted connections, secure
            servers, and restricted access to protect your information.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- COOKIES -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">6. Cookies</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-600">
            FixOra uses cookies to improve user experience, remember login sessions, and analyze
            website traffic. You may disable cookies in your browser settings.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- RIGHTS -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">7. Your Rights</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc ml-6 text-slate-600 space-y-1">
            <li>Request access to your personal data</li>
            <li>Request correction or deletion</li>
            <li>Withdraw consent anytime</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- CHILDREN -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">8. Children's Privacy</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-600">
            Our services are not intended for children under 18. We do not knowingly collect
            personal data from minors.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- UPDATES -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">9. Policy Updates</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-600">
            We may update this Privacy Policy occasionally. Continued use of FixOra means you accept
            the revised policy.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- CONTACT -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">10. Contact Us</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-600">
            If you have questions, contact us at
            <a href="mailto:support@fixora.com" class="text-indigo-600 hover:underline">
              support@fixora.com
            </a>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <!-- FOOTER -->
    <%- include("../partials/client/footer.ejs") %> <%-
    include("../partials/client/profile-script.ejs") %> <%- include("../partials/toast-script.ejs")
    %>
  </body>
</html>
